{"tid":1036173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[乜又係你呀]租飛機未如期付款 香港航空遭追1.46億元","createTime":"2019-02-25T04:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T05:27:41.000Z","uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"28de3beab3a4f35797f82cf97a954d6f5c2eb2d8","tid":1036173,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190225/59299797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190225%2F59299797&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8Y%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=e5269fae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190225%2F59299797&h=c6667027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190225/59299797</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屢有債主臨門的香港航空，再被興訟追債。兩間飛機租賃公司早前向港航出租共6架飛機，但港航未有如期於上周四繳款，涉及共1.46億元。兩公司上周聯袂入稟高等法院，向港航追債及索償。<br />\n<br />\n原告公司分別為總部設於美國、全球最大租賃及銷售飛機公司國際租賃財務公司（International Lease Finance Corporation）及愛爾蘭註冊公司Wilmington Trust Sp Services（Dublin）Limited。兩公司分別向港航出租兩架及四架飛機，分別涉款4,600萬元及1億元。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀稱，兩間原告公司與港航先後於2007年至2017年訂立租賃協議，繳款日為本月21日。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCA285/19】"},{"pid":"53ad5a1ac38456cdf25126a6691f513af1d37a05","tid":1036173,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"今次應該係A350無交租"},{"pid":"9bd22b70854df18c42da7afaca9e8ce27bbc45f0","tid":1036173,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f4fdd08ceb894c534154ccb1c3c2bbba6473d0","tid":1036173,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190225/bkn-20190225113530295-0225_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190225%2Fbkn-20190225113530295-0225_00822_001.html&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8Y%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=ff9d56cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190225/bkn-20190225113530295-0225_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n近期傳出陷入財困消息的香港航空，被指自去年12月開始拖欠租賃飛機費用，遭兩間公司入稟高等法院追討約1917萬美元(約1.5億港元)欠款和利息。兩名原告依次是美國註冊公司International Lease Finance Corporation和愛爾蘭註冊公司Wilmington Trust SP Services (Dublin) Limited，被告是香港航空有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指稱，根據首原告和被告於2007年4月24日簽訂的兩份租賃飛機協議，被告由今年1月開始拖欠首原告款項，截至入稟前欠款總額共約601.5萬美元。另外，根據次原告和被告於2016年5月24日至2017年9月15日期間簽訂的四份租賃飛機協議，被告由去年12月開始拖欠原告款項，截至入稟前欠款總額共約1315.5萬美元。兩名原告於於上周五(22日)入稟向被告追討欠款和利息。"},{"pid":"4e5aed7eacab5eab30f0529d2e9e44dc9a21ddaa","tid":1036173,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf70cc6982101b8232d2bd06ab155a2b4431969d","tid":1036173,"uid":6604,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"啲飛機係憑我自己嘅實力租返嚟"},{"pid":"00c01f6633c9ea35751366a82cf3120690f07780","tid":1036173,"uid":8439,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"bf70cc6982101b8232d2bd06ab155a2b4431969d","tid":1036173,"uid":6604,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"啲飛機係憑我自己嘅實力租返嚟"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"點解我要交租"},{"pid":"b030d339aea5c4f4d439da039218d82154e8bf75","tid":1036173,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00c01f6633c9ea35751366a82cf3120690f07780","tid":1036173,"uid":8439,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"bf70cc6982101b8232d2bd06ab155a2b4431969d","tid":1036173,"uid":6604,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"啲飛機係憑我自己嘅實力租返嚟"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"點解我要交租"},"citedBy":0,"rep